BMAD METHOD™ ATTRIBUTION

The BMAD Method (Breakthrough Method for Agile AI-Driven Development) is a
framework created and maintained by the BMAD Code Organization.

Original BMAD Method: https://github.com/bmad-code-org/BMAD-METHOD
Documentation: https://docs.bmad-method.org/
Website: https://bmadcodes.com/bmad-method/
YouTube: @BMadCode
Discord: https://discord.gg/gk8jAdXWmj

This plugin is an independent Claude Code harness that implements the BMAD
Method planning and orchestration workflows using native Claude Code features
(skills, agents, hooks). It is NOT an official BMAD Code Organization product
and no endorsement is implied.

All credit for the BMAD methodology, agent roles, workflow patterns, document
shapes, and concepts belongs to the BMAD Code Organization and its contributors.
